{"TopicId":206894,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Make LED Strips?","CreatedByName":"Fossilized","CreatedById":207534,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-13T16:35:01Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Fossilized","CreatedById":207534,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-13T16:35:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello, I\u0027m trying to create my own LED strips and place them in the game. I\u0027ve done modding before and successfully gotten them in the game, but am struggling to make them glow. The best I had was a round light source, like a light bulb. In unity and blender I changed my light to an area light, and now I\u0027m getting no light in game. How can I make these strips glow as an LED strip would?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-13T19:31:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts been awhile, and I\u0027m no expert, but IIRC, area lights dont work in KSP..?? Need to be point or spot...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aerodynamic Kerbal","CreatedById":211338,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-13T19:49:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis isn\u0027t Ikea after all...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-02-13T19:51:00Z\u0022 title=\u002202/13/2022 07:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 13, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Aerodynamic Kerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-13T20:42:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved to add-on discussion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-14T10:06:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is an old mod that has them ....\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fossilized","CreatedById":207534,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-23T17:36:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224091545\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206894\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644833172\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022190933\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022zer0Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/14/2022 at 5:06 AM, zer0Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is an old mod that has them ....\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you have the link?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224091334\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022206894\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221644780669\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/13/2022 at 2:31 PM, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts been awhile, and I\u0027m no expert, but IIRC, area lights dont work in KSP..?? Need to be point or spot...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, that makes sense. Gotta line up some spotlights.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wasml","CreatedById":120438,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-25T22:07:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve seen some LED stip mods before but I believe they didn\u0027t actually emit light - they just used an emissive animation so they appeared to glow.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDate